#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn11.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn11.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 11 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn11.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Yajamānasutta "
msgstr "16. Sponsoring Sacrifice "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn11.16:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak Mountain. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.16:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sakko devānamindo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "And then Sakka, lord of gods, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "

msgctxt "sn11.16:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho sakko devānamindo bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn11.16:2.1"
msgid "“Yajamānānaṃ manussānaṃ, "
msgstr "“For humans, those merit-seeking creatures, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:2.2"
msgid "puññapekkhāna pāṇinaṃ; "
msgstr "who sponsor sacrifices, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:2.3"
msgid "Karotaṃ opadhikaṃ puññaṃ, "
msgstr "making merit with attachments, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:2.4"
msgid "kattha dinnaṃ mahapphalan”ti. "
msgstr "where is a gift very fruitful?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.501, sc3
msgctxt "sn11.16:3.1"
msgid "“Cattāro ca paṭipannā, "
msgstr "“Four practicing the path, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:3.2"
msgid "cattāro ca phale ṭhitā; "
msgstr "and four established in the fruit. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:3.3"
msgid "Esa saṅgho ujubhūto, "
msgstr "This is the upright Saṅgha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:3.4"
msgid "paññāsīlasamāhito. "
msgstr "with wisdom, ethics, and immersion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn11.16:4.1"
msgid "Yajamānānaṃ manussānaṃ, "
msgstr "For humans, those merit-seeking creatures, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:4.2"
msgid "Puññapekkhāna pāṇinaṃ; "
msgstr "who sponsor sacrifices, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:4.3"
msgid "Karotaṃ opadhikaṃ puññaṃ, "
msgstr "making merit with attachments, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.16:4.4"
msgid "Saṅghe dinnaṃ mahapphalan”ti. "
msgstr "what is given to the Saṅgha is very fruitful.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
